---
import { siteConfig } from '../config/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Sriman Tirupathy Eshwarappa">
	<section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-24">
		<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-start">
			<div class="lg:w-2/3">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-left">The Architectural <span class="text-gradient">Manifesto</span></h1>
				<p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed italic border-l-2 border-accent/40 pl-6 bg-accent/5 py-4 rounded-r-lg">
					"Architecture is not about drawing boxes; it is about managing the entropy of a growing business through technical wisdom."
				</p>
				<div class="space-y-6 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
					<p>
						For nearly two decades, I have operated at the intersection of business strategy and engineering excellence. As a Principal Architect, my mission is to ensure that technology is never the bottleneck for innovation. 
					</p>
					<p>
						Whether delivering the identity layer for India's national ecosystem (**Aadhaar/UIDAI**) or orchestrating global integration hubs with **MuleSoft and Solace**, my focus remains on **Scalability, Security, and Speed**.
					</p>
					<p>
						My current frontier is the **Agentic Enterprise**. I am pioneering workflows that leverage LLMs not just for code completion, but for high-level architectural reasoning, automated quality engineering, and delivery acceleration.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Leadership Principles</h2>
				<div class="space-y-4">
					<div class="p-6 glass rounded-2xl border border-white/10 group hover:border-accent/30 transition-all">
						<h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
							Pragmatic Radicalism
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400">Respect the legacy systems that run the business, but ruthlessly modernize any component that hinders agility.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 glass rounded-2xl border border-white/10 group hover:border-accent/30 transition-all">
						<h3 class="text-accent font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
							The AI-Augmented Lifecycle
						</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400">Moving beyond manual QA toward intelligent, self-healing quality engineering fueled by GenAI and semantic observability.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			{siteConfig.headshot?.enabled && (
				<div class="lg:w-1/3 w-full order-first lg:order-last">
					<div class="glass p-2 rounded-[2.5rem] sticky top-32">
						<div class="aspect-square rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden bg-slate-800">
							<img 
								src={siteConfig.headshot.src} 
								alt={siteConfig.headshot.alt} 
								class="w-full h-full object-cover filter grayscale"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6 text-center">
							<div class="text-white font-bold mb-1">Sriman T. E.</div>
							<div class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest text-slate-500">Associate Director â€“ Integrations</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			)}
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
